  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Falling Trees</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>dark summer </l>
          <l>falling trees </l>
          <l>dreams hover on ocean breeze </l>
          <l>we smiled at times </l>
          <l>tending to wonder </l>
          <l>and then we sighed and said goodbye </l>
          <l>and sobered </l>
          <l>my mornings are estranged </l>
          <l>my future is around the bend </l>
          <l>and days go by, facing this hunger </l>
          <l>they always try but I deny </l>
          <l>and slumber </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>feel the wind </l>
          <l>it spins you around </l>
          <l>take it in and stay on the ground </l>
          <l>the coast is clear behind this fear </l>
          <l>I never watched it at all </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>long hours deep within </l>
          <l>the anchor is sinking in </l>
          <l>it holds me down, underachieving </l>
          <l>and all this time it questions my believing </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>see the jester taking the crown </l>
          <l>I can try and turn it around </l>
          <l>the falling trees and ocean breeze </l>
          <l>we never left them at all</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
